org.apache.flink.runtime.event.job

Class RecentJobEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.event.job.AbstractEvent
      • org.apache.flink.runtime.event.job.RecentJobEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IOReadableWritable, ManagementEvent

    public final class RecentJobEvent
extends AbstractEvent
implements ManagementEvent
    A RecentJobEvent provides a summary of a job which is either currently running or has been running recently.
